#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.100"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.100:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.100:0.2"
msgid "10. Asuravagga "
msgstr "10. Demons "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.100:0.3"
msgid "100. Potaliyasutta "
msgstr "100. With Potaliya the Wanderer "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.100, sc1
msgctxt "an4.100:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho potaliyo paribbājako yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. "
msgstr "Then the wanderer Potaliya went up to the Buddha, and exchanged greetings with him. "

msgctxt "an4.100:1.2"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho potaliyaṃ paribbājakaṃ bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one side, and the Buddha said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.100:2.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, potaliya, puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "“Potaliya, these four people are found in the world. "

msgctxt "an4.100:2.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.100:2.3"
msgid "Idha, potaliya, ekacco puggalo avaṇṇārahassa avaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā hoti bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena, no ca kho vaṇṇārahassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā hoti bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena. "
msgstr "One person criticizes those deserving of criticism at the right time, truthfully and substantively. But they don’t praise those deserving of praise at the right time, truthfully and substantively. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.100:2.4"
msgid "Idha pana, potaliya, ekacco puggalo vaṇṇārahassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā hoti bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena, no ca kho avaṇṇārahassa avaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā hoti bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena. "
msgstr "Another person praises those deserving of praise … But they don’t criticize those deserving of criticism … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.100:2.5"
msgid "Idha pana, potaliya, ekacco puggalo neva avaṇṇārahassa avaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā hoti bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena, no ca vaṇṇārahassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā hoti bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena. "
msgstr "Another person doesn’t praise those deserving of praise … Nor do they criticize those deserving of criticism … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.100:2.6"
msgid "Idha pana, potaliya, ekacco puggalo avaṇṇārahassa ca avaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā hoti bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena, vaṇṇārahassa ca vaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā hoti bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena. "
msgstr "Another person criticizes those deserving of criticism at the right time, truthfully and substantively. And they praise those deserving of praise at the right time, truthfully and substantively. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.100:2.7"
msgid "Ime kho, potaliya, cattāro puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "These are the four people found in the world. "

msgctxt "an4.100:2.8"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, potaliya, catunnaṃ puggalānaṃ katamo te puggalo khamati abhikkantataro ca paṇītataro cā”ti? "
msgstr "Of these four people, who do you believe to be the finest?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.101, sc3
msgctxt "an4.100:3.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bho gotama, puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.100:3.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.100:3.3"
msgid "Idha, bho gotama, ekacco puggalo avaṇṇārahassa avaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā hoti bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena, no ca kho vaṇṇārahassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā hoti bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.100:3.4"
msgid "Idha pana, bho gotama, ekacco puggalo vaṇṇārahassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā hoti bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena, no ca kho avaṇṇārahassa avaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā hoti bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.100:3.5"
msgid "Idha pana, bho gotama, ekacco puggalo neva avaṇṇārahassa avaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā hoti bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena, no ca vaṇṇārahassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā hoti bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.100:3.6"
msgid "Idha pana, bho gotama, ekacco puggalo avaṇṇārahassa ca avaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā hoti bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena, vaṇṇārahassa ca vaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā hoti bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.100:3.7"
msgid "Ime kho, bho gotama, cattāro puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.100:3.8"
msgid "Imesaṃ, bho gotama, catunnaṃ puggalānaṃ yvāyaṃ puggalo neva avaṇṇārahassa avaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā hoti bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena, no ca vaṇṇārahassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā hoti bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena; "
msgstr "“Master Gotama, of these four people, it is the person who neither praises those deserving of praise at the right time, truthfully and substantively; nor criticizes those deserving of criticism at the right time, truthfully and substantively. "

msgctxt "an4.100:3.9"
msgid "ayaṃ me puggalo khamati imesaṃ catunnaṃ puggalānaṃ abhikkantataro ca paṇītataro ca. "
msgstr "That is the person I believe to be the finest. "

msgctxt "an4.100:3.10"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

#. VAR: Abhikkantā → abhikkantatarā (mr)
msgctxt "an4.100:3.11"
msgid "Abhikkantā hesā, bho gotama, yadidaṃ upekkhā”ti. "
msgstr "Because, Master Gotama, equanimity is the best.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.100:4.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, potaliya, puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.100:4.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro … pe … ime kho, potaliya, cattāro puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.100:4.3"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, potaliya, catunnaṃ puggalānaṃ yvāyaṃ puggalo avaṇṇārahassa ca avaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā hoti bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena, vaṇṇārahassa ca vaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā hoti bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena; "
msgstr "“Potaliya, of these four people, it is the person who criticizes those deserving of criticism at the right time, truthfully and substantively; and praises those deserving of praise at the right time, truthfully and substantively. "

msgctxt "an4.100:4.4"
msgid "ayaṃ imesaṃ catunnaṃ puggalānaṃ abhikkantataro ca paṇītataro ca. "
msgstr "That is the person I consider to be the finest. "

msgctxt "an4.100:4.5"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "an4.100:4.6"
msgid "Abhikkantā hesā, potaliya, yadidaṃ tattha tattha kālaññutā”ti. "
msgstr "Because, Potaliya, understanding of time and context is the best.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.100:5.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bho gotama, puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.100:5.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro … pe … ime kho, bho gotama, cattāro puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.100:5.3"
msgid "Imesaṃ, bho gotama, catunnaṃ puggalānaṃ yvāyaṃ puggalo avaṇṇārahassa ca avaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena, vaṇṇārahassa ca vaṇṇaṃ bhāsitā bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena; "
msgstr "“Master Gotama, of these four people, it is the person who criticizes those deserving of criticism at the right time, truthfully and substantively; and praises those deserving of praise at the right time, truthfully and substantively. "

msgctxt "an4.100:5.4"
msgid "ayaṃ me puggalo khamati imesaṃ catunnaṃ puggalānaṃ abhikkantataro ca paṇītataro ca. "
msgstr "That is the person I believe to be the finest. "

msgctxt "an4.100:5.5"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "an4.100:5.6"
msgid "Abhikkantā hesā, bho gotama, yadidaṃ tattha tattha kālaññutā. "
msgstr "Because, Master Gotama, understanding of time and context is the best. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an4.100:6.1"
msgid "Abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama. "
msgstr "Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent! "

msgctxt "an4.100:6.2"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bho gotama, nikkujjitaṃ vā ukkujjeyya, paṭicchannaṃ vā vivareyya, mūḷhassa vā maggaṃ ācikkheyya, andhakāre vā telapajjotaṃ dhāreyya: ‘cakkhumanto rūpāni dakkhantī’ti; evamevaṃ bhotā gotamena anekapariyāyena dhammo pakāsito. "
msgstr "As if he were righting the overturned, or revealing the hidden, or pointing out the path to the lost, or lighting a lamp in the dark so people with good eyes can see what’s there, Master Gotama has made the teaching clear in many ways. "

msgctxt "an4.100:6.3"
msgid "Esāhaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmi dhammañca bhikkhusaṅghañca. "
msgstr "I go for refuge to Master Gotama, to the teaching, and to the mendicant Saṅgha. "

msgctxt "an4.100:6.4"
msgid "Upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti. "
msgstr "From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.100:6.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.100:6.6"
msgid "Asuravaggo pañcamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an4.100:7.1"
msgid "Asuro tayo samādhī, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.100:7.2"
msgid "chavālātena pañcamaṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.100:7.3"
msgid "Rāgo nisanti attahitaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.100:7.4"
msgid "sikkhā potaliyena cāti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "an4.100:7.5"
msgid "Dutiyo paṇṇāsako samatto. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
